INSTALL

Prerequisites: A C-compiler (e.g. `gcc`) and `make`

Clone and compile

    $ git clone https://github.com/nylander/Resample_fasta.git
    $ cd Resample_fasta
    $ make
    $ make test
    $ sudo make install

Change installation destination by changing PREFIX.
For example:

    $ PREFIX=$HOME make install

Alt. using `cmake`

    $ cd Resample_fasta
    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make
    $ make test
    $ make install

